name: Cpu cooler
description: A CPU cooler is device designed to draw heat away from the system CPU and other components in the enclosure.

name: Keyboard
description: A keyboard is a peripheral device that enables a user to input text into a computer or any other electronic machinery.

name: Mouse
description: A mouse is a small device that a computer user pushes across a desk surface in order to point to a place on a display screen and to select one or more actions to take from that position.

name: Monitor
description: A monitor is an electronic visual computer display that includes a screen, circuitry and the case in which that circuitry is enclosed.

name: Motherboard
description: The motherboard is the backbone that ties the computer's components together at one spot and allows them to talk to each other.

name: Ram
description: RAM is the super-fast and temporary data storage space that a computer needs to access right now or in the next few moments.
